Hitman is a 2007 French-American-British action-thriller film directed by Xavier Gens and based on the video game series of the same name .
The story revolves around Agent 47 , a professional hitman , who was engineered to be an assassin by the group known as `` The Organization '' .
He becomes ensnared in a political conspiracy and finds himself pursued by both Interpol and Russian intelligence .
The film stars Timothy Olyphant , Olga Kurylenko and Dougray Scott and was released on November 21 , 2007 in the United States , November 30 , 2007 in the United Kingdom and December 26 , 2007 in France .
Though critically not well-received , it was a financial success , grossing $ 99 million against a $ 24 million budget .
A sequel was canceled during the production , but it was followed by a reboot titled Hitman : Agent 47 starring Rupert Friend as Agent 47 , released on August 21 , 2015 .